DESCRIPTION:
When provided with a String, capitalize all vowels

For example:

Input : "Hello World!"

Output : "HEllO WOrld!"

Note: Y is not a vowel in this kata.


function swap (string) {
  //We can replace each instance of a vowel using regex: the brackets [] will search for any given vowel within the // within the passed string, and g will search for all instead of stopping at the first encountered
  return string.replace(/[aeiou]/g, x=>x.toUpperCase())
}
